    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "I will use the workaround - however - XDG is not a macOS spec spec, but if a macOS user went through the trouble of setting the environment variable, then they probably want it to be used. Git, for example, uses XDG_CONFIG_HOME on macOS if it is set. And I think we're all happier for it.\n"
